data.description: This beautiful home rests upon an oversized lake view and boasts 2,032 sqft with 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and features an open concept design with a 2-car garage. This home comes with luxury features, granite surfaces, crown molding, diagonal tile throughout the main living areas, stainless steel appliances, blinds on the windows and it’s built by high standards. The home is located in one of Southwest Florida’s very popular gated communities Bella Vida. The community is located just miles from Fort Myers downtown River District and features resort style amenities. Bella Vida features a resort style heated pool, fitness center, clubhouse, lighted tennis, state of the art playground, and much more. Don’t miss out on your chance to own this gorgeous home today in Bella Vida.
